<p><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><br />Ask Eve...</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14pt;">HR Questions & Answers with Eve Clennell of Eden HR Consulting.</span><br /><br />The articles below are published monthly in the West Sussex County Times Business Matters supplement where Eve, our Principle Consultant, is the resident HR expert. The column is entitled ‘Ask Eve’ and readers are invited to pose HR related questions of Eve. The column has been running since October 2007 and she is the longest standing contributor in the magazine. The topics posed are varied and cover a wide range of HR related topics and so are an invaluable resource to the readers.<br /><br />Browse the précis of the articles below and then click on the link to go to the full article.<br /><br />Please note that as Legislation changes bi-annually (in April and October) and as such for articles that have been written prior to 6 months of reading may or may not be out of date. However, if you wish to know more or wish to check that the information contained within any article is correct, please feel free to contact Eve Clennell directly on 01403 734455, 07980 570465 or by email 
